# Uploads Directory

This directory stores temporary uploaded files during processing.

## Important Notes

- Files are automatically cleaned up after processing
- Do not store permanent files here
- Ensure proper permissions for read/write access
- Files are moved to Firebase Storage for permanent storage

## Security

- All files are validated before processing
- File types are restricted to supported formats
- Size limits are enforced
- Files are scanned for security issues

## Structure

```
uploads/
├── temp-file-1.pdf
├── temp-file-2.jpg
└── .gitkeep
```

Files in this directory are temporary and will be deleted after processing completes.
